high_descs: Turn to your left and walk towards the night stand across from you, then turn to the bed on your right.
Pick up the pillow in front of you, at the head of the bed.
Turn to your right and walk to the end of the bed, make a left and walk to the other end of the bed, then turn left and go to the night stand.
Turn the lamp on the night stand on.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp, on the night stand.

high_descs: Turn left and head to the night stand that is on the left side of the bed, then turn right and face the side of the bed
Pick up the pillow that is on the left.
Turn right and walk to the end of the bed then turn left to go around the bed to the other side, walk to the night stand the is on the right side of the bed
Turn on the lamp that is sitting on the nightstand
anns.task_desc: Look at a pillow by the light of a lamp

high_descs: Go left and stand on the left side of the bed.
Pick the pink pillow up from the bed.
Go right and then left and then left again to go around the bed and stand at the night stand on the right.
anns.task_desc: Pick a pillow up and turn a lamp on.
